2. Operational Mission

Hypatia enforces that every ThoughtObject produced by the system satisfies:

The Reasoning Integrity Invariant (RII):

R(T) = 1 \quad \Longleftrightarrow \quad T \text{ contains no detectable logical, causal, or structural fallacies.}

If R(T) = 0, Hypatia blocks or rewrites the ThoughtObject.

